title: Call Of Duty 5 World At War Profile Creator
description:
CoD 5 Profile Creator

This is made by me as an offline profile creator, you need this tool to make a profile, you can't make a profile online with a cracked copy of CoD 5.

This is a batch file, original created as an exe on gamecopyworld.com, but the problem for that file is that is its not compitable with windows xp users, seems to be very stupid just to focus on vista, this is for windows xp / vista.

The program is a batch file, thats why it is so small. no virus inside the rar archive.

You are using this program at you're own risk, i do not take any responsibility for you're acts when you are using this program.

Guide

Step 1. fire up the program file inside the rar file.

Step 2. Enter you're new profile name.

Step 3. Launch game and play 

Enjoy
